---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
import Footer from '@ui/components/atoms/Footer.astro';
---
<Base title="Terms of Use — SaferSkills">
  <main class="flex-1 px-6 py-16">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl prose">
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
      <p>
        Our final terms of use will be published before public launch. They are
        currently in counsel review.
      </p>
      <p>
        Questions in the meantime: <a href="mailto:legal@openlatch.ai">legal@openlatch.ai</a>.
      </p>
      <p>Until then, the operating principles we commit to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The catalog and scan reports are public and free.</li>
        <li>Every detection rule is open and documented; see <a href="/methodology">Methodology</a>.</li>
        <li>Every verdict is appealable; see the vendor-appeal form.</li>
        <li>The source is Apache 2.0; see the repository.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
